divs: Sighting Detailsthey like you, or they wouldn't be joking around with you. keep looking for them. you never know what you might see. when i first started to see THEM they usually took the form of a balloon that would disappear like magic. but i've also seen cudle fish and lobsters like this one,(see attatchment) appear in the sky and then disappear. and sometimes they talk to me, how's that for insane.
